('spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety:mcq:fe0e797f', 'spanish', 'spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety', '8.2 Social Media and Online Safety', 'mcq', 'mcq', 1, '{"question": "Careful — ‘la red’ on its own (as in ‘la red social’) means…", "options": ["network", "the colour red", "a red warning sign", "a type of red fruit grown in Spain"]}'::jsonb, '{"answer": 0, "explain": "False friend! ‘red’ = network, not the colour red. The obvious guess is the trap."}'::jsonb),
('spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety:mcq:3d1c62b0', 'spanish', 'spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety', '8.2 Social Media and Online Safety', 'mcq', 'mcq', 1, '{"question": "Which sentence gives GOOD online safety advice?", "options": ["No se debe compartir datos personales", "Se debe compartir tu contraseña con todos tus amigos", "Se debe compartir datos personales sin cuidado", "No hay que proteger tu contraseña nunca"]}'::jsonb, '{"answer": 0, "explain": "‘no se debe compartir datos personales’ is sound advice; the rest recommend unsafe behaviour."}'::jsonb),
('spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety:mcq:644ed5e9', 'spanish', 'spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety', '8.2 Social Media and Online Safety', 'mcq', 'mcq', 1, '{"question": "Complete: ‘Es importante ___ tu contraseña.’", "options": ["proteger", "protejo", "protegido", "protegiendo"]}'::jsonb, '{"answer": 0, "explain": "‘es importante’ takes an infinitive → proteger. The others are conjugated / non-finite forms."}'::jsonb),
('spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety:mcq:2469a68a', 'spanish', 'spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety', '8.2 Social Media and Online Safety', 'mcq', 'mcq', 1, '{"question": "What is ‘un seguidor’?", "options": ["a follower", "a private message", "a strong password", "a photo album shared online"]}'::jsonb, '{"answer": 0, "explain": "un seguidor = a follower, from the verb seguir (to follow)."}'::jsonb),
('spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety:mcq:31d5aad8', 'spanish', 'spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety', '8.2 Social Media and Online Safety', 'mcq', 'mcq', 1, '{"question": "‘Paso demasiado tiempo en línea’ means…", "options": ["I spend too much time online", "I never go online at all", "I spend only a little time online", "I spend my time offline with friends"]}'::jsonb, '{"answer": 0, "explain": "‘paso demasiado tiempo en línea’ = I spend too much time online. Every distractor changes the amount or negates it."}'::jsonb),
('spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety:mcq:a873b11d', 'spanish', 'spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety', '8.2 Social Media and Online Safety', 'mcq', 'mcq', 1, '{"question": "Higher: ‘Es importante que tengas cuidado’ uses which verb form?", "options": ["the subjunctive (tengas)", "the ordinary present tense (tienes)", "the simple future tense (tendrás)", "a direct command form (ten)"]}'::jsonb, '{"answer": 0, "explain": "‘es importante que’ triggers the subjunctive: tengas, not tienes."}'::jsonb),
('spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety:mcq:feb5c33f', 'spanish', 'spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety', '8.2 Social Media and Online Safety', 'mcq', 'mcq', 1, '{"question": "Which describes the safest online habit?", "options": ["proteger la contraseña y no compartir datos personales", "compartir la contraseña con cualquier desconocido que conoces en línea", "publicar todos los datos personales en el perfil", "aceptar como amigo a cualquier desconocido en línea"]}'::jsonb, '{"answer": 0, "explain": "Protecting your password and not sharing personal data is safe practice; the others describe risky behaviour."}'::jsonb),
('spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety:tf:7ed49132', 'spanish', 'spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety', '8.2 Social Media and Online Safety', 'tf', 'tf', 1, '{"question": "‘la red social’ means ‘social network’ — ‘red’ here is not the colour red."}'::jsonb, '{"answer": true, "explain": "red = network in this context, a common false friend."}'::jsonb),
('spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety:tf:6bd65190', 'spanish', 'spanish:8-2-social-media-and-online-safety', '8.2 Social Media and Online Safety', 'tf', 'tf', 1, '{"question": "‘compartir’ means ‘to share’."}'::jsonb, '{"answer": true, "explain": "compartir = to share, e.g. compartir fotos."}'::jsonb),
